t license may be required.</li><li>Practical experience with design software.</li><li>Experience in design recommended.</li><li>Excellent problem-solving and troubleshooting skills.</li><li>Strong written, verbal, and telephonic communication skills.</li><li>Excellent research and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Strong analytical skills.</li><li>Willingness to work overtime if required.</li></ul>",
